		"description": "GraphQL API for Employee Management System\n\nStudent ID: 101504303\nAuthor: Uzma Shaikh\n\nInstructions:\n1. Run 'npm install' to install dependencies\n2. Run 'npm start' to start the server\n3. Server will run on http://localhost:4000\n4. GraphQL endpoint: http://localhost:4000/graphql",
